        experienceNote: "Qanoni's financial regulatory expertise covers the full range of SAMA and CMA regulatory requirements applicable to Saudi financial institutions — from initial licensing through to regulatory enforcement defense. We provide practical, commercially oriented regulatory advice that enables clients to operate compliantly and efficiently in Saudi Arabia's rapidly evolving financial regulatory environment.",
