        experienceNote: "Online fraud cases in Saudi Arabia require urgent action: for victims, early legal intervention maximizes asset recovery prospects; for accused parties, early criminal defense advice minimizes criminal exposure. Qanoni is available for immediate consultation via WhatsApp or email — 24/7 for urgent fraud matters — providing the rapid response that online fraud cases demand.",
